        "content": "<p><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/wA1QVtyGHXkxz_JhOYQBsBUb/image.png\">image.png</a> <br>\nI couldn't see how this do with axiom of choice ... neither can I understand its meaning ....</p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/3121/wA1QVtyGHXkxz_JhOYQBsBUb/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/3121/wA1QVtyGHXkxz_JhOYQBsBUb/image.png\"></a></div>",
